    "created_at": "2015-02-17T16:09:48Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-02-17T16:09:48Z",
    "body": "If this is an issue about adding a stream which deals with `\\n` and `\\r\\n` differences (as @retep998 mentioned) then it now belongs in the RFC repo because the raw `io::File` will likely not handle it by default but would instead require a wrapper.\n",
